1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 23=

4
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,840
For the two of us

5
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:12,040
to live peacefully by His Majesty's side
in the future,

6
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:15,079
one person must be sacrificed.

7
00:01:16,770 --> 00:01:17,799
Don't lay a finger on him.

8
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,480
That depends on
whether Lu Jianglin can get it done.

9
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:21,560
He's an idiot.

10
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,719
Only you would use him.

11
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:23,840
What do you know?

12
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:24,760
I used him because...

13
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,740
Because of Shen Nanqiao?

14
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,359
She claimed she was reborn.

15
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,159
You...

16
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,480
You knew?

17
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,239
You have the Prince of Jin as leverage,

18
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:38,200
but you don't know
how to use him wisely.

19
00:01:38,210 --> 00:01:39,890
I was the one
who let him leave the palace

20
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,719
to draw Nangong Xuanyu's
attention away.

21
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,680
You captured Shen Nanqiao
and Lu Jianglin,

22
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:49,400
then sent Lu Jianglin to me?

23
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,159
You were using me.

24
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:53,680
If I hadn't been cleaning up your messes
all these years,

25
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,790
do you think
you could've sat securely on that throne?

26
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,590
You refuse to take your medicine,

27
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,920
hurting yourself to look sick

28
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,040
and make others pity you.

29
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,040
How ludicrous.

30
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,079
Of course I can't compare
to Shen Zhinian,

31
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,200
who's good at seducing men.

32
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,560
Chen,

33
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,240
don't tell me you've fallen for her?

34
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,000
Fallen for her?

35
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,080
Your Highness,

36
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,879
do you know

37
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,560
why Nangong Xuanyu suffers so much?

38
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,759
Why?

39
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,599
Because he has been loved.

40
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,520
His mother loved him.

41
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,680
Madam Lian loved him.

42
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,479
Even Shen Zhinian loves him.

43
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,439
He knows what love feels like,

44
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,719
so he craves it.

45
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,719
I'm different.

46
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,080
I've never been loved.

47
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:47,159
And I don't need such a thing.

48
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,520
Your Highness, pull yourself together.

49
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,479
Before His Majesty returns,

50
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,719
we must finish what needs to be done.

51
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,919
You're right.

52
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,719
Those who need to die
must be dealt with.

53
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,000
Once His Majesty returns,

54
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,960
everything will go back
to how it was before.

55
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:17,240
No matter how much Chen wants to use me,

56
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:21,360
surely he wouldn't go so far
as to kill me.

57
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:24,759
How dare you kick me?

58
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:26,280
I've lived through two lifetimes,

59
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,919
and no one has ever dared
kick me before.

60
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,240
Your Ladyship,
what's that supposed to mean?

61
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:33,840
Nothing.

62
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:35,879
You're truly a jinx.

63
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,670
Getting involved with a jerk like him
was bad enough,

64
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,180
and now you've dragged me into it too.

65
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:42,080
Thank you for saving me again,
Your Ladyship.

66
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,840
I wasn't saving you.

67
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:45,520
I was saving myself.

68
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:47,719
I know

69
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:49,439
you're not heartless.

70
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,360
I threw you into
the imperial prison before,

71
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,800
and you still think I'm not heartless?

72
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,319
Let me tell you something.

73
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,680
My heart

74
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,599
is the cruelest,

75
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,719
the most vicious,

76
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:05,159
and the most ruthless of all.

77
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,879
A truly ruthless person

78
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,919
would've executed me

79
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:12,120
the first time

80
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:13,439
they caught me.

81
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:14,560
They wouldn't have

82
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,719
merely forced me

83
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,040
to grow flowers.

84
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,279
That's re-education through labor.

85
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,680
It's how things are done in my hometown.

86
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,510
It was meant to teach you a lesson.

87
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,600
You two vicious women!

88
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,800
Untie me!

89
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:36,040
Didn't you say I was your master?

90
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,319
I'll grant you death today.

91
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,519
Your Ladyship,

92
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,639
I've told you everything I know.

93
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,759
What more do you want?

94
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:45,220
How do I know
whether you're still hiding something?

95
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:47,279
Shen Nanqiao died
six months after entering the palace

96
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,279
in the previous life.

97
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:49,560
That's all she knew.

98
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,240
Rebirth?

99
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,990
Your Ladyship,
could you step aside for a moment?

100
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,319
I'd like to speak with him alone.

101
00:04:56,530 --> 00:04:57,639
I want to listen to it too.

102
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,720
To be honest,

103
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,240
I was reborn as well.

104
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,800
What?

105
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,399
In the previous life,

106
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:15,040
you and I were husband and wife.

107
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:18,480
Shen Nanqiao made a mistake,

108
00:05:18,690 --> 00:05:20,920
and the entire Shen family
was implicated and executed.

109
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,839
After learning the news,

110
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,839
you handed me a letter of repudiation

111
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,279
and personally brought the decree

112
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:28,560
and send me to my demise.

113
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,639
Impossible.

114
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,480
That can't be true.

115
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,920
Now do you understand
why I broke off the engagement?

116
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,399
Talk about perfect timing, Eunuch Pan.

117
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:43,399
Arrest this wretched man.

118
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,800
Get them.

119
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:52,560
Your Majesty,

120
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,690
the Duke Zhen's troops
have been stopped.

121
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:57,150
But they claim the military tally
was handed to Her Highness.

122
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,360
Are you sure it was Her Highness

123
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,720
and not Jiang Chen?

124
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,319
They insist it was given to the Empress.

125
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,120
(It was given to the Empress...)

126
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:09,199
(Could events really unfold
exactly as Shen Zhinian predicted?)

127
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,519
(Nangong Xuanyu executes Jiang Chen)
That's not right.

128
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,959
After Shen Nanqiao died
in the previous life,

129
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,839
Jiang Chen continued living just fine.

130
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,519
You never gave the order

131
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,839
to execute him either.

132
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,360
Could the final note

133
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,879
have been fake?

134
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,240
You mean

135
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:28,319
the mastermind
deliberately left true information

136
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,800
in the first two notes,

137
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:32,680
so that we'd believe the third as well?

138
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,680
It's possible.

139
00:06:36,330 --> 00:06:37,200
Return to the palace.

140
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,879
Why am I so unlucky?

141
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:46,480
I've been captured again.

142
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:48,970
And locked in the same room
as this jerk.

143
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,360
Tough luck.

144
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,879
Save your strength.

145
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,480
You're a walking disaster.

146
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,720
I must've been cursed to ever meet you.

147
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,959
You've already been reborn once.

148
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,290
Why would you still enter the palace?

149
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:03,199
You think life in the palace
is so wonderful?

150
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,920
Whether life is good or bad

151
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,500
depends on how you choose to live it.

152
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,879
We're about to die.

153
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,040
Happy now?

154
00:07:12,090 --> 00:07:14,000
I never thought
that after living two lifetimes,

155
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:16,240
I'd still end up dying this miserably.

156
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:19,040
What do you mean?

157
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:21,360
Are you reborn too?

158
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,439
You could say that.

159
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:29,399
Forget about me.

160
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:31,120
Think of a way out first.

161
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:32,639
The Empress is a lunatic.

162
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:34,120
Who knows how she plans to kill me?

163
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,360
I don't think it's come to that yet.

164
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:37,720
Her Highness

165
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,800
wouldn't really kill us.

166
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,480
That makes sense.

167
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,520
His Majesty will come save you,
won't he?

168
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,240
Little White Snake,

169
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,199
you're here.

170
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:53,920
Ah!

171
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,879
Snake!

172
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,480
It jumped onto you.

173
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:58,240
It's His Majesty's snake.

174
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,319
Little White Snake,

175
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,399
did the scent of herbs
on the prayer beads

176
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,439
lure you here?

177
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,199
Could you bring your master here?

178
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,720
You still remembered to visit me?

179
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:28,279
Father.

180
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,560
Have some tea.

181
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,399
What does Nangong Xuanyu plan

182
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:39,360
to do to me?

183
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:42,519
I command 200,000 cavalry.

184
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,840
If anything happens to me,

185
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,759
they'll march straight to the capital.

186
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,679
Does he really dare touch me?

187
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:50,360
Father,

188
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,080
sometimes I truly hate you.

189
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,320
You forced me to marry him,

190
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:57,120
but you also made him my enemy.

191
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,480
You left me trapped

192
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,559
in the middle.

193
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,480
I married you to him

194
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,440
so we could control him

195
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,840
and use him for our case.

196
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,320
But look at you.

197
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:08,240
Useless fool.

198
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,279
Utterly useless.

199
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,120
You hesitated

200
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,080
and wavered.

201
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:15,200
If you'd rebelled outright back then,

202
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,940
perhaps this empire
would've belonged to the Jiang family.

203
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:20,279
But you feared rebelling
without justification

204
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,420
and being branded a traitor.

205
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:23,120
So you brought Nangong Xuanyu back.

206
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,360
And now that he's grown powerful,

207
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,120
you can't accept it.

208
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,320
Shut it.

209
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:31,559
Even your brother wouldn't dare speak
to me that way.

210
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,480
You forced him

211
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:37,679
to kill his mentor
whom he respected most.

212
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,960
He has hated you for a long time.

213
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,360
Let me tell you one more thing.

214
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:47,440
Your trusted aides have handed
the military tally over to me.

215
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,480
The 200,000 soldiers of yours

216
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,960
will now be under my command.

217
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,919
You!

218
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,519
The tea is poisoned.

219
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:10,799
You...

220
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,200
I'll do as you always wanted, Father.

221
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,919
I'll recover,

222
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:20,240
bear a child,

223
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,600
and serve as

224
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,080
his Empress.

225
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,960
Have you dealt with them?

226
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,440
Who exactly has been dealt with, Empress?

227
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:53,280
What are you talking about,
Your Majesty?

228
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,600
I don't understand.

229
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:56,480
It doesn't matter.

230
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:58,240
Wen Ling, go look for them.

231
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:58,600
Move.

232
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,679
Your Majesty,

233
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:01,879
what is this?

234
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:04,480
I'm searching for Shen Zhinian
and Lady Liu.

235
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,159
Why would they be here with me?

236
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,519
Our marriage

237
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:10,639
was part of Duke Zhen's scheme
from the very beginning.

238
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:12,900
Back when I was
gravely ill and unconscious,

239
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,720
he said I needed a wedding
for good fortune

240
00:11:14,830 --> 00:11:16,279
and sent you into the Eastern Palace.

241
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,799
Before I ascended the throne, I asked

242
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,900
whether you wanted to leave.

243
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,279
I told you I could protect you for life.

244
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,320
Once I married you,

245
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,480
I became your wife.

246
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,240
Why would I leave?

247
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,039
I gave you the position of Empress.

248
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,480
But I wanted your heart.

249
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,840
My heart?

250
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,600
What you've always wanted

251
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:35,399
was supreme power.

252
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,639
Wasn't it?

253
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,960
So in the end,

254
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,759
you only want Shen Zhinian.

255
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:41,720
Yes.

256
00:11:41,879 --> 00:11:43,120
What is so good about her?

257
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,200
Everything.

258
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,240
I love her.

259
00:11:48,639 --> 00:11:49,440
Your Majesty,

260
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,240
you're heartless.

261
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:53,759
Your Majesty,

262
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,559
we found Little White Snake.

263
00:11:56,799 --> 00:11:57,759
You found her?

264
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,790
Keep watch over her.

265
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,600
Yes.

266
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,039
You should be on your way now.

267
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:14,799
At least you'll have company
on the road to the underworld.

268
00:12:17,519 --> 00:12:18,879
Don't worry.

269
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:21,120
You'll be next soon enough.

270
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,759
His Majesty's men are almost here.

271
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,799
Make it quick, then.

272
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,200
Zhinian,

273
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,960
this isn't our past life anymore.

274
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:44,320
I truly

275
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:46,519
love you.

276
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,720
I'll repay you with my life.

277
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,440
Please don't hate me anymore.

278
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,960
Die!

279
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:20,620
♪Moon sets on palace walls,
breeze hits the gates♪

280
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:27,420
♪Falling at first sight,
a life of turmoil wasted♪

281
